00:26:51,114 --> 00:26:53,582
when I can get rid of this
stupid, horrible equipment?

265
00:26:53,690 --> 00:26:57,238
The American top doctor praised
your muscle a great deal.

266
00:26:57,345 --> 00:26:59,423
And what else did they say?

267
00:26:59,538 --> 00:27:05,070
