in your body to be found.

268
00:27:05,177 --> 00:27:07,539
He can't believe how strong you are.

269
00:27:07,649 --> 00:27:10,188
Yes, you're injured,

270
00:27:10,295 --> 00:27:15,054
but with your body's condition
and strong willpower,

271
00:27:15,168 --> 00:27:17,910
it just might be a miracle.

272
00:27:18,023 --> 00:27:19,376
A miracle?

273
00:27:20,878 --> 00:27:24,843
Linda, don't beat around the bush.

274
00:27:28,153 --> 00:27:30,301
Please tell me the truth.

275
00:27:31,913 --> 00:27:33,539
