277
00:27:35,393 --> 00:27:36,639
Tell me!

278
00:27:40,511 --> 00:27:44,024
Bruce, listen to me.

279
00:27:44,131 --> 00:27:48,167
Linda, I can handle it.

280
00:27:48,274 --> 00:27:50,292
Just tell me the truth.

281
00:27:52,243 --> 00:27:54,818
You should.

282
00:27:56,386 --> 00:27:58,569
You should tell me the truth...

283
00:27:58,683 --> 00:28:01,282
