284
00:28:01,398 --> 00:28:03,095
Right?

285
00:28:03,208 --> 00:28:04,762
Bruce...

286
00:28:04,879 --> 00:28:07,763
You tell me now.

287
00:28:08,882 --> 00:28:11,172
Bruce, I... I...

288
00:28:11,284 --> 00:28:14,026
Is it true or not?

289
00:28:22,216 --> 00:28:25,658
Don't you ever,
ever come see me again.

290
00:28:25,766 --> 00:28:27,819
Get out!

291
00:28:27,925 --> 00:28:30,287
You get out of here!

292
00:28:54,312 --> 00:28:57,897
<i>The next couple is Bruce Lee
and Kim Jaman.</i>

293
00:28:58,002 --> 00:29:02,132
