294
00:29:43,430 --> 00:29:45,970
He was great.
- Notice he really mastered the steps.

295
00:30:05,013 --> 00:30:08,170
<i>The champion of the Hong Kong
Cha-Cha Competition</i>

296
00:30:08,286 --> 00:30:13,046
<i>is the couple of Bruce Lee
and Kim Jaman.</i>

297
00:30:16,118 --> 00:30:20,498
Bruce Lee, you felt good today,
didn't you?

298
00:30:20,609 --> 00:30:22,663
So what? You want to fight?

299
00:30:22,767 --> 00:30:25,960
Right. I'll make
an Asian man kiss my ass.

300
00:30:29,103 --> 00:30:30,420
Don't be rude.

301
00:30:30,530 --> 00:30:31,680
Get him!

302
00:30:42,992 --> 00:30:45,046
Come on. Let's go.

303
00:30:45,151 --> 00:30:47,893
Let's get a couple of pies tonight.

304
00:30:52,183 --> 00:30:53,642
You dirty Asian.

305
00:31:00,990 --> 00:31:03,768
Blair, you just wait.

306
00:31:16,725 --> 00:31:18,256
You dirty Asian.

307
00:31:34,618 --> 00:31:35,768
James.

308
00:31:38,621 --> 00:31:40,461
Why'd you get up so early?

309
00:31:40,571 --> 00:31:43,205
You have to go back to the U.S. Soon.

310
00:31:43,321 --> 00:31:45,670
I just want to learn more moves from you
while you're in Hong Kong.

311
00:31:45,770 --> 00:31:49,026
So what do you think
about that, James?

312
00:31:49,135 --> 00:31:52,232
Okay. Go practice standing method.

313
00:31:52,337 --> 00:31:53,691
All right.

314
00:32:03,407 --> 00:32:06,220
You have to practice every morning.

315
00:32:06,331 --> 00:32:09,809
Don't even miss one day.

316
00:32:09,917 --> 00:32:11,543
I know that,

317
00:32:11,657 --> 00:32:14,364
but I want to learn
something more practical.

318
00:32:14,477 --> 00:32:18,228
You're too anxious. Relax.

319
00:32:18,342 --> 00:32:22,792
Anxiety is a big mistake
when practicing kung fu.

320
00:32:22,902 --> 00:32:24,848
I am anxious.

321
00:32:24,955 --> 00:32:29,513
Bruce, if you really want to
master this technique for yourself,

322
00:32:29,621 --> 00:32:34,107
it's not one or two days
or not even one or two years.

323
00:32:34,216 --> 00:32:39,189
Besides, to have
a real perception of kung fu,

324
00:32:39,297 --> 00:32:43,048
you need to have
a superb perseverance.

325
00:32:43,162 --> 00:32:45,310
If you don't have that,

326
00:32:45,425 --> 00:32:47,715
then you'll have nothing
when you get old.

327
00:32:47,826 --> 00:32:50,117
Do you understand me?

328
00:33:07,878 --> 00:33:10,132
Take it.

329
00:33:10,245 --> 00:33:11,870
What's up?

330
00:33:11,986 --> 00:33:14,241
What, are you waiting
for revenge or something?

331
00:33:14,353 --> 00:33:16,537
Or are you waiting for my fists?

332
00:33:16,651 --> 00:33:18,704
But I should warn you,
these are well-trained fists.

333
00:33:18,809 --> 00:33:20,792
I've come to teach you a lesson today.

334
00:33:20,898 --> 00:33:22,595
A lesson.

335
00:33:24,135 --> 00:33:26,675
Then let's find a place.

336
00:33:26,781 --> 00:33:28,407
Right here.
- Oh, really?

337
00:33:28,521 --> 00:33:30,599
If you kick my ass,
I'll fix my bike myself.

338
00:33:30,714 --> 00:33:32,340
Got it?

339
00:33:32,455 --> 00:33:34,638
Are you out of your mind?

340
00:33:34,753 --> 00:33:38,468
Okay. It looks like you need
another lesson from me.

341
00:33:39,592 --> 00:33:41,217
Come on.

342
00:33:41,332 --> 00:33:43,314
I'll let teachers and students see

343
00:33:43,421 --> 00:33:46,304
how a whitey like you falls in front of me.

344
00:33:48,260 --> 00:33:49,541
Get him! Come on!
- Get him!

345
00:33:55,396 --> 00:33:57,057
Honey!

346
00:34:02,253 --> 00:34:03,535
Bruce!

347
00:34:03,646 --> 00:34:05,629
Do you see that? I'll beat him

348
00:34:05,735 --> 00:34:08,548
down on the dirty ground
and let you guys step over him.

349
00:34:10,087 --> 00:34:11,403
Come on!

350
00:34:22,966 --> 00:34:24,627
Bruce...

351
00:34:24,742 --> 00:34:26,795
There goes your children's future.

352
00:34:33,688 --> 00:34:36,715
You embarrass this family!
- No. Stop. Stop. Bruce...

353
00:34:36,821 --> 00:34:39,919
Bruce, just apologize
to your father. Hurry up.

354
00:34:40,024 --> 00:34:42,006
Dad, why don't you listen
before you punish me?

355
00:34:42,113 --> 00:34:43,572
No...
- There's no need.

356
00:34:43,680 --> 00:34:45,175
I've known everything.

357
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:47,357
I told you not to fight, for God's sake,

358
00:34:47,474 --> 00:34:49,801
and I swear to God,
I'll punish you if you do.

359
00:34:49,910 --> 00:34:51,536
You heard me.

360
00:34:51,652 --> 00:34:53,764
But I didn't promise you
I wouldn't fight today.

361
00:34:53,879 --> 00:34:56,063
You bastard!
- Stop! Please stop!

362
00:34:56,176 --> 00:34:59,132
Just run away, Bruce, please. Just stop it.
- All you know is fight.

363
00:34:59,240 --> 00:35:01,222
Stop it! Enough! Please just go!
- Come here!

364
00:35:01,328 --> 00:35:04,035
All you know is fight!
- Stop!

365
00:35:04,148 --> 00:35:06,855
Stop, please!
- You're spoiled!

366
00:35:06,968 --> 00:35:09,116
Dad, what's with you?
- Enough!

367
00:35:09,231 --> 00:35:11,902
You can't hit Mom.
You can't ever do that to her.

368
00:35:12,016 --> 00:35:14,093
It's okay, Bruce honey. It's fine.

369
00:35:14,209 --> 00:35:17,889
Even if you beat me to death,
I won't run away,

370
00:35:18,003 --> 00:35:19,772
even if I really want to.

371
00:35:19,883 --> 00:35:21,961
You feel like it?

372
00:35:22,076 --> 00:35:24,403
You dare talk back to me
after making such trouble?

373
00:35:24,513 --> 00:35:26,068
Stop it!
- Bruce!

374
00:35:26,184 --> 00:35:28,652
Stop beating him.
- I'm telling you...

375
00:35:28,760 --> 00:35:30,742
I am telling you...
- Help us. Stop beating him.

376
00:35:30,848 --> 00:35:32,474
- Okay. Dad,
- Please.

377
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:37,183
I swear to you I won't fight again.

378
00:35:37,289 --> 00:35:43,342
But how can I fight back
if someone insults me?

379
00:35:43,450 --> 00:35:46,548
I mean, look, son,
today you were at the school

380
00:35:46,653 --> 00:35:49,015
where you picked a fight
with your own classmate Blair.

381
00:35:49,125 --> 00:35:52,460
But he insulted me yesterday
on Udang Street.

382
00:35:52,571 --> 00:35:57,224
Do you understand
what that feels like?

383
00:35:57,340 --> 00:36:00,782
He also broke my sister's bike.

384
00:36:00,891 --> 00:36:04,404
He did it on purpose,
and I didn't even pick the fight.

385
00:36:04,512 --> 00:36:06,137
The bike is broken.

386
00:36:06,252 --> 00:36:07,711
Dad can fix it.

387
00:36:07,819 --> 00:36:09,314
Can you make no more trouble?

388
00:36:10,499 --> 00:36:11,888
You must've offended him,
you see?

389
00:36:11,996 --> 00:36:14,180
I didn't!

390
00:36:14,294 --> 00:36:16,477
I didn't do anything wrong.

391
00:36:16,591 --> 00:36:19,297
He's jealous 'cause I'm
the champion of cha-cha.

392
00:36:19,411 --> 00:36:21,524
He's British,

393
00:36:21,638 --> 00:36:23,549
and I'm Chinese!

394
00:36:23,658 --> 00:36:26,257
I don't deserve to win the title?

395
00:36:30,307 --> 00:36:32,669
Son, I'm sorry.

396
00:36:35,772 --> 00:36:37,682
We are all Chinese.

397
00:36:37,791 --> 00:36:39,939
We are a nation of etiquette.

398
00:36:40,054 --> 00:36:44,125
Can you not learn to hold back
or be tolerant?

399
00:36:44,231 --> 00:36:49,584
Dad, he called me a dirty Asian, Dad!

400
00:36:49,697 --> 00:36:53,483
The son of a dirty Asian!

401
00:37:37,702 --> 00:37:41,038
Why are you fighting
with your clothes?

402
00:37:55,804 --> 00:37:57,749
What's with you?

403
00:37:57,858 --> 00:37:59,697
What do you want?

404
00:38:01,304 --> 00:38:04,675
Hey, Bruce, we better go.

405
00:38:09,033 --> 00:38:10,765
Better to fight with a pro.

406
00:38:14,323 --> 00:38:17,421
You are the one I want to fight.

407
00:38:17,526 --> 00:38:19,081
You want to fight?

408
00:38:20,450 --> 00:38:21,981
Hey, come on.

409
00:39:10,475 --> 00:39:12,029
Stop there.

410
00:39:13,572 --> 00:39:15,590
What was that?

411
00:39:17,645 --> 00:39:19,140
Kung fu.

412
00:39:19,247 --> 00:39:21,846
Go and learn some kung fu.

413
00:39:23,911 --> 00:39:25,964
Kung fu?

414
00:39:27,497 --> 00:39:29,336
Kung fu?

415
00:39:57,644 --> 00:40:00,872
Hoi-chuen, I'd like to tell you

416
00:40:00,986 --> 00:40:05,508
that it seems like your son Bruce

417
00:40:05,615 --> 00:40:08,534
has made up his mind
to learn kung fu.

418
00:40:08,644 --> 00:40:10,483
Is that right?

419
00:40:12,021 --> 00:40:15,321
Hoi-chuen, when you didn't
allow him to learn kung fu,

420
00:40:15,433 --> 00:40:16,963
I totally agreed.

421
00:40:17,068 --> 00:40:20,855
Indeed, it's hard
for kung fu artists to live.

422
00:40:20,967 --> 00:40:22,498
Why bother to learn?

423
00:40:22,603 --> 00:40:24,229
But I had a chat with him tonight.

424
00:40:26,363 --> 00:40:28,345
And your son Bruce, you know,

425
00:40:28,452 --> 00:40:31,715
the only thing
he thinks about day and night

426
00:40:31,829 --> 00:40:34,677
is learning kung fu.

427
00:40:34,788 --> 00:40:36,556
I'm afraid this time,

428
00:40:36,668 --> 00:40:38,436
neither you nor I can sway him.

429
00:40:40,357 --> 00:40:43,063
You know, the saying goes,

430
00:40:43,177 --> 00:40:45,919
a father knows his son.

431
00:40:46,032 --> 00:40:48,571
Let me ask you.
Do you really know him?

432
00:40:48,677 --> 00:40:51,312
He's my son.
How can I not know him?

433
00:40:51,427 --> 00:40:53,125
That's bull crap!

434
00:40:56,301 --> 00:40:58,591
Tø be frank, Bruce is smart.

435
00:40:58,703 --> 00:41:01,730
When he dedicates himself to something,
he does it completely.

436
00:41:01,836 --> 00:41:04,578
When he studies it,
he learns it faster than anyone else.

437
00:41:04,691 --> 00:41:07,575
That's right. For example, cha-cha.

438
00:41:07,684 --> 00:41:10,497
Do you know why
he wanted to learn cha-cha?

439
00:41:10,609 --> 00:41:13,006
Hoi-chuen, you don't get it.

440
00:41:13,115 --> 00:41:14,574
I'll tell you why and what.

441
00:41:14,682 --> 00:41:16,830
Because all those
foreign classmates

442
00:41:16,945 --> 00:41:18,404
were looking down on him,

443
00:41:18,510 --> 00:41:21,085
so he wanted to prove
that he could do it, too.

444
00:41:22,305 --> 00:41:23,765
Yes, but my Bruce...

445
00:41:23,872 --> 00:41:26,578
he never committed
to one thing whatsoever.

446
00:41:26,691 --> 00:41:29,230
You see, he won
the champion of cha-cha.

447
00:41:29,337 --> 00:41:30,618
Right?
- Exactly.

448
00:41:30,730 --> 00:41:32,355
But now he doesn't want to continue.

449
00:41:32,470 --> 00:41:34,345
This is what
you don't understand about him.

450
00:41:37,309 --> 00:41:39,219
I think from now on,

451
00:41:39,329 --> 00:41:44,231
we should get
a real kung fu master.

452
00:41:44,341 --> 00:41:46,774
Someone to train him.

453
00:41:48,553 --> 00:41:50,143
James,

454
00:41:50,259 --> 00:41:54,496
if Bruce really wants
to learn kung fu,

455
00:41:54,611 --> 00:41:58,920
then you'll be the best for him.

456
00:41:59,031 --> 00:42:01,250
Why bother to get a master?

457
00:42:01,364 --> 00:42:04,877
Tø tell you the truth, Hoi-chuen,

458
00:42:04,984 --> 00:42:07,346
if Bruce is really up for kung fu,

459
00:42:07,456 --> 00:42:09,604
then I can't teach him.

460
00:42:09,719 --> 00:42:13,469
I'm not among the top masters
in Hong Kong.

461
00:42:13,582 --> 00:42:16,288
I'd like to introduce him right away

462
00:42:16,402 --> 00:42:20,295
to the head of Yong Chun
Boxing Academy, Master Ye.

463
00:42:40,805 --> 00:42:42,609
It's 1:30 a.m. Already.

464
00:42:42,719 --> 00:42:44,702
What the hell's going on here?

465
00:42:52,363 --> 00:42:54,725
It's way too late for this.

466
00:42:54,834 --> 00:42:56,887
What's wrong with him?

467
00:43:00,822 --> 00:43:02,697
Let's go.

468
00:43:35,355 --> 00:43:37,194
Hey, who are...

469
00:43:37,304 --> 00:43:39,701
Hey, who are you?

470
00:43:39,811 --> 00:43:41,200
What do you want?
- What the hell?

471
00:43:47,051 --> 00:43:49,935
Hello, Master Wang.

472
00:43:50,045 --> 00:43:51,361
What do you want?

473
00:43:51,472 --> 00:43:55,638
I would like to practice
with Yellow Skin.

474
00:43:57,982 --> 00:44:00,035
Come practice with him.

475
00:44:31,610 --> 00:44:33,449
Yeah! Nice!
- That was great!

476
00:44:33,560 --> 00:44:35,708
Good job!
- You got him!

477
00:44:39,373 --> 00:44:41,212
Very good! Yes!

478
00:45:29,640 --> 00:45:30,790
Dad.

479
00:45:32,356 --> 00:45:35,691
Bruce, get your clothes and come.

480
00:45:35,802 --> 00:45:37,499
I'll take you to see someone.

481
00:45:38,866 --> 00:45:41,335
Come on. Follow me.

482
00:45:56,376 --> 00:45:58,001
Dad, please.

483
00:45:58,116 --> 00:46:00,443
Follow me. Quickly.

484
00:46:05,288 --> 00:46:06,818
Faster.

485
00:46:10,475 --> 00:46:12,208
Stay with me. Quickly.

486
00:46:48,036 --> 00:46:51,027
Dad, what is this all about?

487
00:46:51,134 --> 00:46:53,709
Bruce, you didn't give up.

488
00:46:53,815 --> 00:46:55,440
Good for you.

489
00:47:02,414 --> 00:47:05,155
Master Ye, I brought my son to you.

490
00:47:05,268 --> 00:47:07,178
Based on your instruction,

491
00:47:07,287 --> 00:47:10,587
I let him run over here
from Kingburg Park.

492
00:47:10,698 --> 00:47:13,060
And my son... he made it.

493
00:47:13,170 --> 00:47:14,630
Well, that's good.

494
00:47:14,736 --> 00:47:18,213
Not so many people
can run such a distance in one go.

495
00:47:18,322 --> 00:47:22,286
He's passed the first test
for acceptance?

496
00:47:24,692 --> 00:47:27,196
All right. Come on back.

497
00:47:43,282 --> 00:47:45,015
Yong Chun Quan,

498
00:47:45,126 --> 00:47:48,319
created by Master Wu Mei
from Fujian.

499
00:47:48,434 --> 00:47:50,582
The key thing is
it's simple and practical.

500
00:47:50,696 --> 00:47:54,340
They're practicing an entree routine
called "small idea."

501
00:47:56,301 --> 00:47:58,283
All right.

502
00:47:58,390 --> 00:47:59,565
You guys spread out.

503
00:47:59,678 --> 00:48:01,897
Small combat. Three groups.

504
00:48:03,299 --> 00:48:04,959
Yong Chun Quan

505
00:48:05,074 --> 00:48:07,543
requires coordination
of hands and feet,

506
00:48:07,650 --> 00:48:09,632
including three-side fist...

507
00:48:09,739 --> 00:48:11,721
...breakthrough fist.

508
00:48:13,708 --> 00:48:15,785
The steps include clam step,

509
00:48:15,901 --> 00:48:17,846
tripod step, chasing step,

510
00:48:17,954 --> 00:48:20,660
and also one leg standing.

511
00:48:20,774 --> 00:48:22,304
And another thing is,

512
00:48:22,410 --> 00:48:24,629
what you see is striking fists.

513
00:48:24,742 --> 00:48:27,970
That means you launch attack
while defending.

514
00:48:29,267 --> 00:48:31,736
What he's doing is chasing step,

515
00:48:31,844 --> 00:48:34,871
which requires speed and ferocity.

516
00:48:36,752 --> 00:48:39,494
This is grab and strike,
used when you are close.

517
00:48:39,606 --> 00:48:42,146
Yong Chun Quan is integrated

518
00:48:42,252 --> 00:48:45,516
with Nanquan and close-fighting fists.

519
00:48:45,629 --> 00:48:47,540
It stresses actual combat.

520
00:48:47,648 --> 00:48:50,639
Shun Leung, come.

521
00:48:50,747 --> 00:48:53,073
Show Bruce the inch punch.
Over here.

522
00:48:53,183 --> 00:48:54,678
Get a board.

523
00:48:57,604 --> 00:48:59,859
Inch punch means one burst

524
00:48:59,972 --> 00:49:03,413
at all the strength to beat
his rival within an inch.

525
00:49:03,522 --> 00:49:05,504
Within an inch?

526
00:49:05,611 --> 00:49:08,008
That's right.

527
