02:48:51,948 --> 02:48:56,434
Bruce Lee, I will watch you fall this time.

1802
02:49:08,867 --> 02:49:12,059
Who is it?
- I want to speak to Bruce Lee.

1803
02:49:14,506 --> 02:49:16,001
Hello? Who is it?

1804
02:49:16,107 --> 02:49:18,611
It's me.

1805
02:49:18,718 --> 02:49:20,901
Bruce Lee,

1806
02:49:21,016 --> 02:49:23,615
you may forget everybody,

1807
02:49:23,731 --> 02:49:25,285
but you'll never forget me.

1808
02:49:25,402 --> 02:49:26,577
Yellow Skin.

1809
02:49:29,301 --> 02:49:31,591
Our business is not done yet.

1810
02:49:31,703 --> 02:49:33,471
What the hell do you want?

1811
02:49:33,583 --> 02:49:35,766
You know what I want.

1812
02:49:37,969 --> 02:49:40,295
Yellow Skin, listen up.

1813
02:49:40,406 --> 02:49:42,768
We don't have any
unfinished business anymore.

1814
02:49:42,878 --> 02:49:45,548
Your Master Wang had apologized to me.

1815
02:49:45,662 --> 02:49:47,323
No!

1816
02:49:47,438 --> 02:49:50,630
Back then, I made a big mistake.

1817
02:49:50,745 --> 02:49:52,026
Tø make it up to you,

1818
02:49:52,137 --> 02:49:53,418
I'd like to challenge you again.

1819
02:49:53,530 --> 02:49:55,475
I'll defeat you fairly and openly.

1820
02:49:55,584 --> 02:49:56,734
Otherwise,

1821
02:49:58,681 --> 02:50:02,468
the rest of my life will be meaningless.

1822
02:50:02,580 --> 02:50:04,907
But I don't want to compete with you.

1823
02:50:05,017 --> 02:50:07,000
You're afraid.

1824
02:50:08,220 --> 02:50:09,501
I'm not afraid of you.

1825
02:50:09,612 --> 02:50:12,496
I no longer want to prove myself
through competing.

1826
02:50:12,606 --> 02:50:16,915
What I'm doing is to promote
the way of martial arts.

1827
02:50:17,028 --> 02:50:20,399
I don't give a damn about
your way of martial arts.

1828
02:50:20,508 --> 02:50:22,169
My goal is to defeat you.

1829
02:50:22,284 --> 02:50:24,017
Listen up, Bruce Lee.

1830
02:50:24,129 --> 02:50:26,526
This is it.

1831
02:50:26,636 --> 02:50:28,890
I am now formally challenging you.

1832
02:50:29,003 --> 02:50:33,383
I told that I won't challenge anyone,

1833
02:50:33,493 --> 02:50:36,092
nor take a challenge anymore.

1834
02:50:39,132 --> 02:50:42,396
No! Bruce Lee,
you have to accept my challenge!

1835
02:50:42,509 --> 02:50:44,836
I'll never give up if I don't defeat you!

1836
02:50:48,427 --> 02:50:50,789
Bruce Lee, you will not ignore me! No!

1837
02:51:35,701 --> 02:51:38,799
And?
- 14, 15, 16...

1838
02:51:38,904 --> 02:51:42,381
Bruce? Darling?

1839
02:51:43,917 --> 02:51:45,899
Are you all right?

1840
02:51:46,006 --> 02:51:47,845
I'm fine.

1841
02:51:47,955 --> 02:51:49,580
Come.

1842
02:51:49,696 --> 02:51:53,767
Hey, I've fixed some snacks for you.

1843
02:51:53,873 --> 02:51:55,819
Your mom taught me
how to make dim sum.

1844
02:51:55,926 --> 02:51:59,262
And I know how much you love dim sum.

1845
02:51:59,374 --> 02:52:01,664
Come. Sit down.

1846
02:52:01,775 --> 02:52:03,306
You need to take a break.

1847
02:52:03,411 --> 02:52:04,621
Just rest.

1848
02:52:06,127 --> 02:52:08,346
Sweetie, I don't want
to eat anything right now.

1849
02:52:08,459 --> 02:52:12,138
I just want to lie on your lap
quietly for a while.

1850
02:52:14,342 --> 02:52:16,976
My mind has just
been racing recently.

1851
02:52:17,092 --> 02:52:22,896
I just got so much stuff going on
that I just can't relax, you know?

1852
02:52:23,011 --> 02:52:25,966
These days... These days,

1853
02:52:26,074 --> 02:52:28,578
you seem to have changed
into another person,

1854
02:52:28,684 --> 02:52:32,850
and I think Professor Ino was right.

1855
02:52:32,966 --> 02:52:35,114
I think that you're exhausted
to the point

1856
02:52:35,229 --> 02:52:37,412
where you just need to lay and rest.

1857
02:52:38,606 --> 02:52:40,516
Like you are now.

1858
02:52:41,703 --> 02:52:44,623
Quietly, not thinking of anything.

1859
02:52:44,732 --> 02:52:46,785
Bruce, I'll call the hospital tomorrow

1860
02:52:46,891 --> 02:52:48,968
to set up an appointment
for your checkup.

1861
02:52:49,084 --> 02:52:50,543
And if there's still no diagnosis,

1862
02:52:50,651 --> 02:52:53,155
I'll take you to the States
for an even better checkup.

1863
02:52:53,261 --> 02:52:55,860
No, damn it!

1864
02:52:55,977 --> 02:52:57,436
What are you saying?

1865
02:52:57,543 --> 02:52:59,240
You want me to stop the film?

1866
02:52:59,353 --> 02:53:01,750
So many people on the crew
depend on me,

1867
02:53:01,860 --> 02:53:04,079
and the boss has thrown
so much money into this,

1868
02:53:04,192 --> 02:53:06,826
but you want me
to moan in the hospital,

1869
02:53:06,942 --> 02:53:10,871
having exams,
even a vacation in the States?

1870
02:53:10,980 --> 02:53:12,678
How the hell could I do that?

1871
02:53:17,107 --> 02:53:18,317
Darling.

1872
02:53:22,294 --> 02:53:23,789
Please don't call the hospital again.

1873
02:53:23,895 --> 02:53:25,556
I don't have any disease.

1874
02:53:27,516 --> 02:53:31,587
If I did,
it'd be nothing but a headache

1875
02:53:31,693 --> 02:53:34,470
caused by exhaustion, right here.

1876
02:53:36,183 --> 02:53:38,961
Bruce, your expectation
is way too high.

1877
02:53:39,073 --> 02:53:41,056
You need to calm down.

1878
02:53:51,744 --> 02:53:53,275
Let me.

1879
02:53:54,356 --> 02:53:55,946
Hello?

1880
02:53:56,061 --> 02:53:58,281
Bruce Lee, either you accept my challenge,

1881
02:53:58,393 --> 02:54:00,791
or you admit you lose in public!

1882
02:54:00,900 --> 02:54:02,846
Listen, you insane, crazy devil,

1883
02:54:02,953 --> 02:54:06,016
Bruce does not accept your challenge.

1884
02:54:06,122 --> 02:54:08,756
This is something between us men.

1885
02:54:08,872 --> 02:54:10,498
Nothing to do with you.

1886
02:54:10,612 --> 02:54:13,769
I'm warning you, now leave us alone.

1887
02:54:18,897 --> 02:54:20,843
Bruce, what are you doing?

1888
02:54:20,951 --> 02:54:23,491
Linda, I cannot allow him
to be so arrogant,

1889
02:54:23,597 --> 02:54:25,128
especially right now.

1890
02:54:27,148 --> 02:54:28,916
I have to keep all my dignity.

1891
02:54:29,028 --> 02:54:30,523
Do you understand
what this means to me?

1892
02:54:30,629 --> 02:54:32,255
Bruce...

1893
02:54:32,369 --> 02:54:34,315
Hold on.

1894
02:54:36,581 --> 02:54:40,581
Okay, I'll accept your challenge.

1895
02:54:40,690 --> 02:54:43,229
Please tell me the date and place.

1896
02:54:43,335 --> 02:54:46,398
Listen carefully.

1897
02:54:46,503 --> 02:54:47,749
In just three days,

1898
02:54:47,860 --> 02:54:53,558
I'll invite all the masters
of Honk Kong martial arts,

1899
02:54:53,674 --> 02:54:56,522
and they will see
how the great Bruce Lee...

1900
02:54:56,633 --> 02:54:59,031
loses under my fists!

1901
02:55:00,497 --> 02:55:01,813
All right, Yellow Skin.

1902
02:55:01,924 --> 02:55:04,321
You'll regret this.

1903
02:55:04,431 --> 02:55:05,535
Let me tell you,

1904
02:55:05,650 --> 02:55:08,047
you don't know me at all,

1905
02:55:08,156 --> 02:55:10,138
nor do you understand me.

1906
02:55:10,244 --> 02:55:12,262
You didn't disappoint me.

1907
02:55:13,412 --> 02:55:14,871
I'm telling you,

1908
02:55:14,979 --> 02:55:16,961
I've never been defeated by anyone,

1909
02:55:17,067 --> 02:55:19,916
much less some loser like you.

1910
02:55:23,089 --> 02:55:28,134
Well, let's meet at the arena.

1911
02:55:30,470 --> 02:55:36,666
By then, don't forget to bring
a stretcher for yourself!

1912
02:55:36,770 --> 02:55:39,060
Crazy nut job.

1913
02:56:19,067 --> 02:56:20,692
Bruce Lee!

1914
02:56:22,652 --> 02:56:25,644
We finally meet again.

1915
02:56:28,361 --> 02:56:30,510
Long time no see.

1916
02:56:30,624 --> 02:56:32,772
You still look the same.

1917
02:56:32,886 --> 02:56:36,708
You're still so arrogant.
It seems that you got better in kung fu,

1918
02:56:36,820 --> 02:56:41,794
but I'm not so sure
if you got better ethically.

1919
02:56:41,902 --> 02:56:44,335
I failed to defeat you in the States.

1920
02:56:44,444 --> 02:56:46,497
I've regretted it for many years.

1921
02:56:49,283 --> 02:56:51,716
But today,

1922
02:56:51,824 --> 02:56:53,972
we'll finally decide who the winner is.

1923
02:56:54,087 --> 02:56:56,200
Wait.

1924
02:56:56,315 --> 02:56:59,958
Before we start,
I have a little suggestion.

1925
02:57:00,075 --> 02:57:02,057
We'll compete one round first.

1926
02:57:02,163 --> 02:57:04,347
After the first round,

1927
02:57:04,461 --> 02:57:06,122
if you can't defeat me,

1928
02:57:06,236 --> 02:57:08,491
we'll stop the competition.

1929
02:57:08,604 --> 02:57:10,158
You shut up.

1930
02:57:11,423 --> 02:57:14,021
If you're able,

1931
02:57:14,138 --> 02:57:16,465
let your kung fu speak!

1932
02:57:50,168 --> 02:57:52,672
You've already lost.

1933
02:57:52,779 --> 02:57:55,413
You're doomed to lose this competition.

1934
02:57:55,529 --> 02:57:57,439
You're too eager...

1935
02:57:57,548 --> 02:57:59,387
too eager

1936
02:57:59,498 --> 02:58:00,993
to defeat me.

1937
02:58:01,099 --> 02:58:02,797
You shut up!

1938
02:58:02,909 --> 02:58:04,820
If I were afraid of death,

1939
02:58:04,928 --> 02:58:07,563
I wouldn't have come.

1940
02:58:12,343 --> 02:58:14,811
I'm ready now.

1941
02:58:18,713 --> 02:58:20,588
Let's stop right here.

1942
02:58:22,369 --> 02:58:26,155
It's not a bad thing
to stop at the right time.

1943
02:59:22,662 --> 02:59:24,323
How do you like that?

1944
02:59:26,074 --> 02:59:28,887
For speed, I'm faster.

1945
02:59:28,997 --> 02:59:30,766
For kicking,
I'm tougher than you.

1946
02:59:30,877 --> 02:59:36,646
I've said it long before,
kung fu takes more practicing,

1947
02:59:36,761 --> 02:59:38,600
less yapping.

1948
02:59:38,710 --> 02:59:42,010
Don't instruct me
like a master in front of me!

1949
02:59:42,122 --> 02:59:43,926
Quit your nonsense.

1950
02:59:44,037 --> 02:59:46,054
Just sign it!

1951
02:59:51,834 --> 02:59:53,638
You dare not?

1952
02:59:53,749 --> 02:59:54,899
I will.

1953
03:01:05,808 --> 03:01:09,072
Tøday, you're doomed to die!

1954
03:02:19,365 --> 03:02:21,347
Why don't you say stop?

1955
03:02:23,020 --> 03:02:25,868
Stop, stop, stop!

1956
03:02:25,980 --> 03:02:27,368
Stop! Bruce Lee, you win.

1957
03:02:43,176 --> 03:02:47,176
Yellow Skin, didn't you ask me
about my boxing?

1958
03:02:47,284 --> 03:02:50,512
Well, now I'm telling you.
It's a Chinese martial art

1959
03:02:50,626 --> 03:02:52,845
called...

1960
03:02:52,958 --> 03:02:57,861
Jeet Kune Do.

1961
03:05:21,707 --> 03:05:22,882
Bruce.

1962
03:06:00,139 --> 03:06:06,263
Bruce, you can soar now.

1963
03:07:07,743 --> 03:07:10,662
The 32 years of Bruce Lee's life

1964
03:07:10,771 --> 03:07:14,522
is a journey filled
with extraordinary vitality.

1965
03:07:14,636 --> 03:07:18,351
Bruce Lee has opened
two brand-new fields for us.

1966
03:07:18,465 --> 03:07:21,836
He has contributed to the world
his amazing kung fu

1967
03:07:21,946 --> 03:07:24,830
and his unforgettable films.

1968
03:07:24,939 --> 03:07:29,628
He helped the world discover
authentic Chinese kung fu,

1969
03:07:29,744 --> 03:07:33,459
and Chinese kung fu
has also dazzled the world

1970
03:07:33,573 --> 03:07:36,006
through Bruce Lee's achievement.

1971
03:07:36,114 --> 03:07:38,167
Chinese kung fu movies

1972
03:07:38,273 --> 03:07:40,706
have opened a new and fresh chapter

1973
03:07:40,814 --> 03:07:43,449
because of Bruce Lee.

1974
03:07:43,564 --> 03:07:46,271
We believe, deep in our hearts,

1975
03:07:46,383 --> 03:07:49,896
that the spirit
is the core of a human being.

1976
03:07:50,004 --> 03:07:52,472
The day of death is also the moment

1977
03:07:52,581 --> 03:07:54,314
of coming back to life,

1978
03:07:54,425 --> 03:07:57,273
as the spirit never dies.

1979
03:07:57,384 --> 03:07:59,639
May God bless Bruce Lee

1980
03:07:59,751 --> 03:08:02,350
and accept his soul.

1981
03:08:02,467 --> 03:08:04,271
Amen.

1982
03:08:18,898 --> 03:08:20,844
Don't wake him.

1983
